r\",\r\n      \"score\": 233.077,\r\n      \"summary\": \"本目录包含ArkUI框架和Cangjie语言中Router模块的API参考文档，主要涵盖应用内页面导航的实现与管理。内容涉及通过URL进行页面跳转、替换及返回的操作，详细介绍了Router类的方法（如pushUrl、back）、参数传递机制，以及RouterState类和RouterMode枚举用于管理页面栈状态和路由模式（如Standard和Single）。这些文档适用于使用ArkUI和Cangjie进行鸿蒙应用开发的开发者，旨在指导其正确实现页面路由逻辑和数据传输。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/.abstract.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/.overview.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/Router/.abstract.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/Router/.overview.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/Router/Router_2more_4f7e423e.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-apis-uicontext-router/Router/class_Router.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-introduction/.abstract.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-introduction/.overview.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": null,\r\n      \"doc_kind\": null\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"api_id\": \"arkui.navigation\",\r\n      \"title\": \"Navigation\",\r\n      \"score\": 232.628,\r\n      \"summary\": \"基于仓颉语言的ArkUI框架Navigation组件，作为路由导航根视图容器，管理NavPathStack路由栈，实现页面间的跳转与状态管理。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-switching-navigation/.abstract.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-switching-navigation/.overview.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-switching-navigation/Navigation/.overview.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-switching-navigation/Navigation/基础类型定义/.overview.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-switching-navigation/Navigation/组件属性.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-navigation-navigation/.abstract.md\",\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/Guide/arkui-cj/cj-nav