ArkUI开发的初学者或中级开发者，旨在帮助用户快速掌握评分组件的属性设置、样式自定义及状态绑定技巧。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-button-picker-rating/Rating/示例代码/.abstract.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": null,\r\n      \"doc_kind\": null\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"example_id\": \"example.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-button-picker-slider-slider-1-abstract-md\",\r\n      \"title\": \".abstract\",\r\n      \"score\": 197.759,\r\n      \"summary\": \"本目录展示了如何在ArkUI框架中使用仓颉语言配置和自定义滑动条的基础样式。内容涵盖了OutSet（外置）、InSet（内置）以及垂直方向滑动条的实现，重点演示了气泡、刻度、滑块和滑轨的显示控制。通过style、showTips、blockColor等属性，开发者可以调整交互效果和颜色，并利用onChange回调实现状态双向绑定。该文档适合具备ArkUI基础和仓颉语法知识的开发者，用于学习UI组件的属性配置与状态管理。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-button-picker-slider/Slider/示例代码/示例1滑动条基础样式/.abstract.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": null,\r\n      \"doc_kind\": null\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"example_id\": \"example.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-button-picker-slider-slider-abstract-md\",\r\n      \"title\": \".abstract\",\r\n      \"score\": 197.759,\r\n      \"summary\": \"This directory serves as a comprehensive repository of practical code examples designed to demonstrate UI component implementation using the ArkUI framework and the Cangjie programming language. It focuses primarily on i\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-button-picker-slider/Slider/示例代码/.abstract.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": null,\r\n      \"doc_kind\": null\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"docs\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-abilitykit-cj-apis-ability-access-ctrl-ohosability-access-ctrl-class-atmanager-func-requestpermissionsfromuseruiabilityc-82361e31\",\r\n      \"title\": \"func requestPermissionsFromUser(UIAbilityContext, Array\\\\<Permissions>, AsyncCallback\\\\<PermissionRequestResult>)\",\r\n      \"score\": 284.281,\r\n      \"summary\": \"public func requestPermissionsFromUser(context: UIAbilityContext, permissionList: Array<